    public abstract class AbstractPTPlace<E extends AbstractPTFlowRelation<? extends AbstractPTPlace<E>,? extends AbstractPTTransition<E>>>
extends AbstractPlace<E,java.lang.Integer>
    Abstract class that defines general properties for places of place/transition nets (P/T Nets).
    This class inherits basic Petri net place properties from AbstractPlace.
    It is parameterized with a specialized type of relations which can be added (AbstractPTFlowRelation).
    P/T Nets consider only one token type.
    The state of a P/T Net place is determined by the number of tokens it holds,
    thus the state type is set to Integer.
    作者:
    Thomas Stocker
    另请参阅:
    序列化表格

      • canConsume

        public boolean canConsume(java.lang.Integer state)
        从类复制的说明: AbstractPlace
        Checks, if the place can consume the given state, i.e.
        merging the actual state and the given state does not exceed the places' capacity.
        This method does NOT actually "add" the given state to the places' actual state.
        指定者:
        canConsume 在类中 AbstractPlace<E extends AbstractPTFlowRelation<? extends AbstractPTPlace<E>,? extends AbstractPTTransition<E>>,java.lang.Integer>
        参数:
        state - The state to merge.
        返回:

        false otherwise.

      • getState

        public java.lang.Integer getState()
        从类复制的说明: AbstractPlace
        Returns the state of the place in terms of number and kind of tokens.
        The returned state should NOT be used to manually add or remove tokens from a place.
        Token adding/removal is done by Petri net transitions.

        getState 在类中 AbstractPlace<E extends AbstractPTFlowRelation<? extends AbstractPTPlace<E>,? extends AbstractPTTransition<E>>,java.lang.Integer>
